org.kitteh.irc.client.library.feature

Class CapabilityManager.Defaults

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kitteh.irc.client.library.feature.CapabilityManager.Defaults
  • Enclosing interface:
    CapabilityManager

    public static final class CapabilityManager.Defaults
extends Object
    Contains the capabilities natively supported by KICL, which will be requested automatically upon availability. Defaults defined as transient are not requested unless additional functionality is enabled, as documented here.
